px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DA1MwZQy9wh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">halsey (@iamhalsey) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>早在 6 月，这位歌手就在社交媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-shares-health-update-following-the-release-of-new-song-the-end-3762993">透露，她在 2022 年被诊断出患有狼疮 SLE 和一种罕见的 T 细胞淋巴增殖性疾病。</a>这两者我可能会终生拥有，”她在帖子的标题中写道。 “经历了一个艰难的开始后，在出色的医生的帮助下，我慢慢地控制了一切。两年后，我感觉好多了，我比以往任何时候都更感激有音乐可以听。我迫不及待地想回到属于我的地方：和你们一起唱歌、尖叫，我的心都碎了。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，哈尔西最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/for-my-next-trick-halsey-unveils-the-great-impersonator-album-tracklist-3797194">透露了她即将推出的第五张录音室专辑“伟大的模仿者”的完整曲目列表</a>。该密纹唱片包括之前发行的单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-halsey-debut-new-song-ego-live-at-surprise-intimate-london-koko-gig-3784129">Ego</a> 》、《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-reveals-shes-lucky-to-be-alive-after-health-struggles-as-she-shares-new-single-the-end-3762516">The End》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-halseys-emotive-nine-inch-nails-inspired-new-single-lonely-is-the-muse-3784426">《Lonely Is The Muse》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-was-really-nervous-about-clearing-britney-spears-lucky-sample-shared-everything-with-her-before-release-3780469">《Lucky》</a> ，定于 10 月 25 日发行，<a href="https://www.halseymusicstore.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已开放预购</a>。 《伟大的模仿者》将作为2021年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">《如果我没有爱，我想要权力》</a>的后续作品。</p><p>在对 2021 年唱片的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">四星评价</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“几乎不用说，这张专辑非常激烈，而且并不完全充满轻松的轻松感。这也是只有哈尔西才能做出的错综复杂、无穷无尽的令人信服的艺术宣言。”</p><p>哈尔西此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-says-new-album-is-all-over-the-place-and-full-of-experimentation-3776430">开玩笑说她的新唱片将“无处不在”并且“充满实验”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-recreates-dolly-partons-rainbow-cover-to-kick-off-the-great-impersonator-preview-series-3800438">哈尔西 (Halsey) 重现多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 的《彩虹》封面，为《伟大的模仿者》预览系列拉开序幕，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
惠特尼·休斯顿 (Whitney Houston) 的母亲、福音音乐传奇人物西西·休斯顿 (Cissy Houston) 去世，享年 91 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/whitney-houstons-mother-and-gospel-music-legend-cissy-houston-dead-at-91-3800428?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=whitney-houstons-母亲和福音音乐传奇西西休斯顿去世 91 岁Surej SinghTue, 08 Oct 2024 02:49:32 +0000 Music NewsNews..Soul https://www.nme.com/?p=3800428 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位格莱美获奖福音歌手在她的职业生涯中曾与艾瑞莎·富兰克林、埃尔维斯·普雷斯利和吉米·亨德里克斯合作过</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/whitney-houstons-mother-and-gospel-music-legend-cissy-houston-dead-at-91-3800428">惠特尼·休斯顿 (Whitney Houston) 的母亲、福音音乐传奇人物西西·休斯顿 (Cissy Houston) 去世，享年 91 岁，</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cissy-houston@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>福音音乐传奇人物、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/whitney-houston">惠特尼休斯顿</a>的母亲西西去世，享年 91 岁。</p><p>休斯顿的儿媳帕特·休斯顿在一份声明中证实，休斯顿于周一（10 月 7 日）在接受阿尔茨海默病临终关怀期间去世。 “我们的心充满痛苦和悲伤。我们失去了我们家庭的女族长，”帕特对<a href="https://people.com/cissy-houston-whitney-houston-mom-dead-age-91-alzheimers-disease-7501905" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>说。</p><p> “西西妈妈在我们的生活中一直是一位坚强而崇高的人物。一位有着深厚信仰和信念的女性，非常关心家庭、事工和社区。她在音乐和娱乐领域七年多的职业生涯将永远留在我们心中。” </p><figure id="attachment_3800435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800435" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800435" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/whitney-cissy-houston@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800435" class="wp-caption-text">惠特尼和西西·休斯顿。图片来源：Larry Busacca/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>帕特继续说道：“她对流行音乐和文化的贡献是无与伦比的。我们很幸运并感激上帝允许她与我们一起度过了这么多年，我们感谢她教给我们的许多宝贵的人生课程。愿她与她的女儿惠特尼、孙女博比·克里斯蒂娜以及其他珍贵的家庭成员安息。”</p><p>西西·休斯顿 (Cissy Houston) 原名艾米丽·德林卡德 (Emily Drinkard)，于 1938 年与姐姐安妮 (Anne) 以及兄弟拉里 (Larry) 和尼基 (Nicky) 一起作为声乐组合“德林卡德四人组”(Drinkard Four) 的一员开始了她的音乐生涯。 1963 年，她与侄女 Dee Dee Warwick 组建了一个名为“Sweet Inspirations”的乐队。</p><p> Sweet Inspirations 后来为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dionne-warwick">Dionne Warwick</a> （也是 Cissy 的侄女）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/otis-redding">Otis Redding</a>等人提供了和声，录制了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/van-morrison">Van Morrison</a>的“Brown Eyed Girl”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimi-hendrix">Jimi Hendrix</a>的“Burning of the Midnight Lamp”、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aretha-franklin">Aretha Franklin</a>等曲目。的“Ain&#39;t No Way”，并于 1969 年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley)</a>拉斯维加斯驻场期间支持他。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800436" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800436" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800436" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sweet-inspirations@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800436" class="wp-caption-text"> 1967 年，西西·休斯顿（最右）与《甜蜜灵感》。图片来源：James Kriegsmann/Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 1970 年，艾米丽·德林卡德 (Emily Drinkard) 开始了自己的单飞生涯，将自己更名为西西·休斯顿 (Cissy Houston)。作为一名独奏音乐家，休斯顿很快成为福音音乐界的知名人物，但也为 R&amp;B、灵魂乐和迪斯科项目提供了自己的声音。她荣获两项格莱美最佳传统灵魂福音专辑奖； 1997 年和 1999 年两次。她还为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chaka-khan">Chaka Khan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-simon">Paul Simon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a>等人录制和声。</p><p>西西·休斯顿还曾短暂为她的女儿惠特尼提供现场和声，并出现在惠特尼的多部音乐录影带和电影中。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/whitney-houston-50-1284287">2012 年惠特尼去世</a>后，西西<a href="https://people.com/celebrity/whitney-houstons-death-mom-cissy-houston-opens-up-in-new-book/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">出版了一本回忆录，其中透露了有关已故女儿滥用药物问题的新信息</a>，并表示她“对她独自死去感到愤怒”。</p><p>西西·休斯顿去世的消息传出后，几位音乐家向这位已故的福音传奇人物表示敬意。鲍比·布朗在向<a href="https://people.com/bobby-brown-pays-tribute-former-mother-in-law-cissy-houston-dead-8724628" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志发表</em></a>的关于他前岳母去世的声明中表示：“就这一巨大损失向休斯顿家人致以爱和祝福。愿她在和平与力量中安息。布朗一家。” </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v21.0"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/lonilove/posts/pfbid02TDKESK8WjsAQYYqTfwLJu8WE5aLopgg5Fd9qK1WTJG8DciMDc98GdpKVAnJU584zl" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044193498283/posts/1152565772893195/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>艾米丽·德林卡德（Emily Drinkard），艺名西西·休斯顿（Cissy Houston），是一位美国灵魂乐和福音歌手。休斯顿是一个创始国……</p><p>发布者<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lonilove">Loni Love</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044193498283/posts/1152565772893195/">2024 年 10 月 7 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p><strong><em>这是一个发展的故事</em></strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/whitney-houstons-mother-and-gospel-music-legend-cissy-houston-dead-at-91-3800428">惠特尼·休斯顿 (Whitney Houston) 的母亲、福音音乐传奇人物西西·休斯顿 (Cissy Houston) 去世，享年 91 岁，</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《烈焰红唇》合作者内尔·史密斯去世，年仅 17 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-flaming-lips-collaborator-nell-smith-has-died-ged-17-3800422?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-flaming-lips-collaborator-内尔·史密斯已去世，年龄 17 岁Surej SinghTue, 08 Oct 2024 01:48:17 +0000 Music NewsNews..IndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3800422 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>史密斯于 2021 年与 The Flaming Lips 合作发行了翻唱 Nick Cave 的专辑，目前正在制作 2025 年的首张专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-flaming-lips-collaborator-nell-smith-has-died-aged-17-3800422">《Flaming Lips》合作者 Nell Smith 去世，享年 17 岁的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nell-smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-flaming-lips">The Flaming Lips</a>合作的年轻音乐家 Nell Smith 去世，享年 17 岁。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cocteau-twins">Cocteau Twins</a>的西蒙·雷蒙德在社交媒体上证实并宣布了史密斯的死讯。雷蒙德的 Bella Union 厂牌已与史密斯签约，并将于明年发行她的首张专辑。</p><p>雷蒙德在社交媒体上写道：“周末，我们的艺术家和亲爱的朋友内尔·史密斯在不列颠哥伦比亚省突然悲惨地去世，我们都感到震惊和悲痛。 Nell 年仅 17 岁，正准备于 2025 年初在 Bella Union 发行她的第一张个人唱片，该唱片是与 Penelope Isles 的 Jack 和 Lily Wolter 在布莱顿制作的。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA1ZBTpy-ZY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.8